-- ============================================================================
-- 0022_hs_codes_deletion_seed.sql
--
-- Seeds the is_deleted / deletion_effective_date / replacement_codes columns
-- added by 0021_hs_codes_deletion.sql with data extracted from the SABER
-- platform PDF hscodes-1-2026.pdf (cycles 2025-06-01 through 2025-11-27).
--
-- Why inline the data (not call pnpm db:seed:deleted):
--   Production deploys via migrate-and-start.ts, which only runs Drizzle
--   migrations — there is no postdeploy hook.  Without inlining, every prod
--   release would need an out-of-band seed step. Same pattern as
--   0018_procedure_codes_seed.sql.
--
-- UPSERT-safe: re-running or adding a future 0023_*_seed.sql is safe —
--   existing rows update their fields, new deleted codes are added.
--
-- Source CSV: data/saber-deleted-codes.csv
--   Regenerate with: npx tsx src/scripts/parse-saber-pdf.ts <pdf_path>
--   Re-apply with:   pnpm db:seed:deleted
--
-- 64 deleted codes from 5 SABER notification cycles.
-- ============================================================================

